get_symbols(array, weights, k) → pick k symbols for reels

get_symbol_odds(symbol) → return odds or multiplier for a symbol

get_special_symbols(array) → pick rare/wild symbols

generate_spin_result() → returns full reel result based on weights

Utility / helpers

random_index(array) → return a random index

random_range_dict(dict_of_values) → pick key based on weighted values

seed_rng(seed_value) → reset RNG with a new VRF hash

get_unique_numbers(n, min, max) → unique numbers, like lottery draws

Optional / advanced

draw_lottery(array, k) → special random selection for mini-games

generate_symbol_table() → returns a dict of symbols → payouts → special rules

apply_caps(value, max_value) → helper to enforce max payout per spin